title: Looking for a fifth man in a ranked 5s team Jg/Mid
body:

We mostly play for fun and have been in teams together before and have been put in bronze 5 (so don't expect to be challenjour in 5 games)
If you want in the team add and message me in game.
IGN: i like big black
Sever: OCE
